---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Eyebrow from '../components/Eyebrow.astro';
import Panel from '../components/Panel.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Junu's Lab">
  <section class="block-head">
    <Eyebrow text="ABOUT" />
    <h2>Research-oriented builder profile</h2>
    <p>Junu's Lab is my research-oriented portfolio for computer vision, machine learning, and animal behavior analysis.</p>
    <p>I am an undergraduate student in IT Management at SeoulTech. My long-term interest is to build systems that can understand animal behavior from raw video, moving from pose estimation to behavior recognition and eventually behavior prediction.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="grid cols-3">
    <Panel title="Current focus">
      <ul class="plain">
        <li>Animal pose estimation and keypoint-based behavior analysis</li>
        <li>Video understanding for long animal behavior videos</li>
        <li>Weak / semi-supervised learning for annotation-efficient labeling</li>
      </ul>
    </Panel>
    <Panel title="How I work">
      <ul class="plain">
        <li>Build small reproducible ML/CV experiments</li>
        <li>Track recent papers, datasets, tools, and benchmarks</li>
        <li>Turn research reading into lab notes, project ideas, and portfolio artifacts</li>
      </ul>
    </Panel>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
